External and internal morphology of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Izumi &amp; Fujii" authorityYear="2021" class="Anthozoa" family="Edwardsiidae" genus="Edwardsianthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Edwardsianthus amethystus" order="Actiniaria" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="amethystus">
